snippet.title: Dogs are so funny, they will definitely make you laugh - Funny DOG videos
snippet.description:
Dogs are great, they are man's best friend and the funniest animals! Just look how all these dogs and puppies play, sleep, get along with babies, how they fail, make funny sounds,... So funny, ridiculous and cute! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
